metadata.description:

And that's not all - in the near future, you'll have access to download the high-resolution MP3 files, video files, and JPEG files, so you can fully envelop yourself in the intoxicating atmosphere of "Drug Store". With its trippy and chill vibes, this NFT is the perfect soundtrack for a relaxing evening or an otherworldly escape. So get ready to immerse yourself in the surreal and ethereal world of "Drug Store" - the first of many NFTs that will take you on a mind-bending journey through music and art. Don't miss out on this one-of-a-kind experience - get your hands on "Drug Store" today!
